oices, the survey maker could make the fraudulent case like some people think Obama did poorly during his first year in office while nobody think Trump did poorly during the first year, so Trump is a better president.  %0a%3c %0a%3c Here is a news article talking about Trump's biased inaugural year approval poll: https://www.newsweek.com/trump-fake-poll-doesnt-let-americans-disapprove-white-house-764804%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
